@startuml contextDiagram
!theme plain

actor "Developer" as User

rectangle "VS Code" {
    component "Frank!Framework Extension" as Extension
}

rectangle "External Tools & Resources" {
    component "Frank!Runner" as Runner
    component "Frank!Doc" as Documentation
    component "Frank!Framework Wiki" as Wiki
    component "Docker / Docker Compose" as Docker
    component "Apache Ant" as Ant
}

User -> Extension : Interacts with

Extension ..> Runner : Runs Frank projects
Extension ..> Docker : Deploys via
Extension ..> Ant : Executes build scripts
Extension ..> Documentation : Links component docs
Extension ..> Wiki : Fetches snippets

note right of Extension
  **Features:**
  * Open/Create new Frank projects
  * Run Frank (Ant, Docker, Docker Compose)
  * Manage Frank!Framework versions
  * Visualize Configuration Flowchart
  * Manage/Insert Snippets (Wiki & User)
  * Link to Frank!Doc
end note

@enduml
